CachedPlaceholder - Class in org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.placeholder
A cached placeholder will store the value of the placeholder for each online player.
So if you replace the cached placeholder, you won't get the newest data immediately.
By default, the cached placeholder will renew every 10 seconds.
CachedPlaceholder() - Constructor for class org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.placeholder.CachedPlaceholder
 
CachedSkin - Class in org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.mojang
Represents a cached player skin implementation.
A cached skin is a skin but has an expire time.
The skin data is stored in the folder of this library.
The skin will be renewed automatically when it expired.
